
0.01  05 Sep 2002  Initial release.

0.02  06 Sep 2002  Documented the fact that linewise_rewrite blats
                   any existing tmpfile.

0.03  10 Sep 2002  Documented the fact that killing Perl during the
                   commit breaks it as well as a failed rename, and
                   specified the commit order.

0.04  19 Sep 2002  Fixed warnings during make test and added a
                   reference to File::Transaction::Atomic.

1.00  25 Mar 2003  Bumped version to 1.00.

